The paper deals with image processing and recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The use of robust PCA and sparse representation also suggests that the paper may be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves text recognition, which could be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories.
